long.ar:
Best for extended outreach to rival followers and Instagram email extraction. It helps you automatically export information about followers or followers, including users' emails and phone calls, which is much more valuable.

How to use it?
1. After installing the extension, open the extension.
2. Please log in to your account on the IG website first.
3. Select Export followers or followers.
4. Enter an export Instagram account, such as "apple".
5. Click the Start button to work automatically.
6. Wait a moment, the user information will be displayed below, just export it to csv or excel.

Features:
✓ Free
✓ Unlimited follower/follow export
✓ Extract IG Email address
✓ Export IG followers with one click
✓ Export data to XLS(Excel)/CSV/JSON format
✓ Data is downloaded automatically when ready
✓ Random interval range and wait for a period of time, suitable for downloading large amounts of data
✓ Extract user data, including followers and number of followers, number of posts, profile, public email, phone number, external URL, address, etc.

# Data privacy
Very secure, all data is processed on your local computer, never through our web servers, no one knows what you have exported.

Attention:
To protect your main IG account from temporary restrictions, we strongly recommend creating a dedicated account for data export activities.  This approach helps minimize the risk of interfering with your daily use of IG while keeping your main account safe.
